query:
SELECT MIN(mi_idx.info) AS rating, MIN(t.title) AS movie_title
 FROM info_type AS it,
 keyword AS k,
 movie_info_idx AS mi_idx,
 movie_keyword AS mk,
 title AS t
 WHERE t.id = mi_idx.movie_id
 AND t.id = mk.movie_id
 AND mk.movie_id = mi_idx.movie_id
 AND k.id = mk.keyword_id
 AND it.id = mi_idx.info_type_id
 AND it.info = 'rating'
 AND k.keyword LIKE '%sequel%'
 AND mi_idx.info > '8.0'
 AND t.production_year > 2010;
plan_content: /*+  SeqScan(it) SeqScan(k) IndexScan(mk keyword_id_movie_keyword) IndexScan(t title_pkey) IndexScan(mi_idx movie_id_movie_info_idx) NestLoop(k mk) NestLoop(k mk t) NestLoop(k mk t mi_idx) NestLoop(it k mk t mi_idx) Leading((it (((k mk) t) mi_idx))) */
